public class SpecificationTransformerTypeBased<T extends SpecificationTypeBased,S extends Specification> extends Object implements org.apache.commons.collections15.Transformer<T,S>
Basic Transformer from a SpecificationTypeBased to a Specification. The default Architecture is constructed by connecting one Resource of each type in the ResourceTypes to an unlimited-capacity on-chip bus with Links from the LinkTypes.
